595,IssueCommentEvent,2017-01-07 10:22:31+00:00,52478762,etingof/pysnmp,483385,pontillo,,,199322017,271075221,"Aha. I figured out how to reproduce this in my environment. Curiously, when I went back to re-test, I couldn't get it to happen again with my current code. Then I changed the code I was using to get the `bulkCmd` as follows, and it started happening again:

```
def partial_v2_get_bulk(host, community, port=161):
