2013,IssueCommentEvent,2017-09-29 10:42:23+00:00,95990745,limdauto/drf_openapi,2032984,limdauto,,,261592239,333094003,"@Amoki hey it's in the doc: https://drf-openapi.readthedocs.io/en/latest/usage.html#overwriting-default-permission. Basically 

1 - Don't add `drf_openapi.urls` to your url patterns. So don't do this:

```
urlpatterns += [url(f'{API_PREFIX}/', include('drf_openapi.urls'))]
```

2 - Instead, create an url handler of your own

```
from drf_openapi.views import get_schema_view

url('schema/$', get_schema_view(url='', title=""API Documentation""), name='api_schema')
```

Let me know if that works",{},OWNER,User,False
