2058,IssueCommentEvent,2017-08-17 10:09:57+00:00,12677403,matheuscas/pycpfcnpj,48132,elyezer,,,250779916,323027307,"Six is listed on the requirements file but when you install a lib, usually, you do that by running pip and the dependencies should also be listed on install_requires. For more information check [1]

