2073,IssueCommentEvent,2015-05-02 08:56:06+00:00,6054289,niklasf/python-chess,402777,niklasf,,,72568167,98336169,"Thanks for reporting this, @jackalsh! This wasn't clear to me from the UCI specification, but all engines seam to provide scores relative to the current pv.

The new way to get the score of the best move is:
```
