3725,IssueCommentEvent,2016-05-13 15:59:30+00:00,40684033,mozilla/sops,578466,jbuck,131524,mozilla,154042819,219085642,"I tried with vim instead of bbedit to rule out something strange that it's doing:

```
(assume-aws-role prod)$ EDITOR='vim' sops common.yaml
INFO: assuming AWS role 'arn:aws:sts::361527076523:assumed-role/hiera-sops-prod/sops@jbuckley-23775'
