<details><summary><i>Previously, pacogomez (Paco Gómez) wrote…</i></summary><blockquote>

does it support group as well?
</blockquote></details>

We do not have support for groups in this current implementation.  Groups can only be imported from an LDAP server. Since we do not have support for LDAP yet in the SDK, I didn't add support for the group.  We can have a separate task to import groups and add support of groups in acl.

