4986,IssueCommentEvent,2017-09-13 01:23:08+00:00,3510804,GalSim-developers/GalSim,3650485,jmeyers314,1462196,GalSim-developers,256403081,329029730,"Okay, I think I fixed the invalid evaluation of SEDs inside `calculateFlux` bug, and also deprecated the bolometric flux.

