thanks for being part of the Font Awesome community.

Unfortunately I cannot leave this PR open because:
- Files under the `/less` and `/scss` folders are automatically generated by the sources in [`/src`](https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome/tree/master/src/assets/font-awesome)
