5867,IssueCommentEvent,2017-02-13 04:10:50+00:00,49976939,learningequality/kolibri,2367265,indirectlylit,3926525,learningequality,204693432,279290535,"> I'm not entirely sure what's happening yet, but I can't get the exercise renderer to display under this PR. I see the bird with no errors

This wasn't quite true - turns out there's this warning during the build process:

```
WARNING  assets/src/module.js not found for plugin exercise_perseus_render_module.
```

