6305,IssueCommentEvent,2016-12-27 08:41:18+00:00,71996613,blue-yonder/tsfresh,13162426,MaxBenChrist,6234170,blue-yonder,196477329,269294510,"> I am very happy that @MaxBenChrist added ReasonableFeatureExtractionSettings and
