",{},,User,False
6307,IssueCommentEvent,2018-02-05 11:07:19+00:00,71996613,blue-yonder/tsfresh,13162426,MaxBenChrist,6234170,blue-yonder,292254741,363053128,"From our/my experience, pandas Data Frame are the standard carrier of relational information for data science. pandas is a great package to do analysis on your data. This is why we developed the package in the first place. (we used to heavily rely on pandas `.groupby` in the pas) 

Now, If you have your time series data in numpy arrays, you can just call the pandas Dataframe constructer and use tsfresh on that.  

