8237,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-30 20:21:25+00:00,55808787,openthread/openthread,16142208,jwhui,16142269,openthread,271939795,361722076,"Would be great to add support for the Thunderboard Sense 2 platform.

From your [fork](https://github.com/jobroe/openthread/tree/thunderboard-sense-2), it appears that the only changes are a CPP define and a board path.  Does it make sense to add conditionals in [examples/Makefile-efr32](https://github.com/openthread/openthread/blob/master/examples/Makefile-efr32) and [examples/platforms/efr32/Makefile.am](https://github.com/openthread/openthread/blob/master/examples/platforms/efr32/Makefile.am) based on an environment variable?

